fields.name: Buddy Waggle
fields.description: Treat Dispensing Toy features patented openings at either end of the toy. Each opening contains inner-facing, soft and flexible prongs that allow kibble or treats to be stuffed inside the toy.

fields.name: Elephunk
fields.description: These Busy Buddytoys are designed for longer lasting playtime! Each one is made with a different and unique chewing experience in mind and helps redirect potentially destructive chewing behaviour into positive playtime.

fields.name: Marrow Bone
fields.description: Marron Bone is a durable interactive dog bone that provides hours of enjoyment and chewing satisfaction. It is ideal for strong chewers and features an irresistible jerky flavour down the middle.

fields.name: Shareables Jerky
fields.description: The perfect treat for your dog (and cats too!). That’s because rabbit meat is a “smart” hypoallergenic, high-protein and low-fat novel protein choice for your pet.

fields.name: Core Treat
fields.description: Core are tender, meaty, free of preservatives & contain no wheat, corn, added animal fat, artificial colors or flavours.

fields.name: BioActive Dental Chews
fields.description: Fresh Mouth Dental Chews made with organic Icelandic sea kelp with bacteriostatic properties that works with saliva to fight plaque.

fields.name: Skinny Bakes
fields.description: Daily support for healthy hip and joints with functional ingredients: Glucosamine, Chondroitin, Turmeric.

fields.name: Train Me!
fields.description: Healthy Omega Treats allow your pet to indulge in a five layer treat that is packed with omega-3.

fields.name: Multi Purpose Harness
fields.description: This harness comes equipped with a removable chestplate, optional removable/interchangable side patches (sold separately).

fields.name: Harness and Dog Collar
fields.description: Great deal for big dogs, body harness and collar with name engraved.
